{"tid":60144,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"U12國家打吡 巴塞8秒破皇馬","createTime":"2016-12-30T08:16:42.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-31T00:13:30.000Z","uid":2169,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"897440c93e556733b5cb43de0cc19e137a66bc5c","tid":60144,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:16:42.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=jYQxgPNCiBBMWRoR2vEy0AT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=ec1640b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】巴塞隆拿與皇家馬德里的青年軍小將，哪一方較優秀？近日一場U12比賽，8秒便分勝負！<br />\n<br />\n巴塞隆拿青訓一向人才輩出，近年便培育了美斯、沙維及恩尼斯達等世界著名球星，反觀皇家馬德里較多購入外援來支撐，自家青訓產品通常被變賣。近日一場U12的青少年盃賽4強，兩軍對壘，也證明巴塞的未來棟樑較出色。<br />\n<br />\n比賽時間與一般球賽不同，只踢40分鐘，但巴塞U12僅用了8秒鐘，便藉敵軍控球失誤，由沙維柏拉拿斯後腳妙傳，交給有「新美斯」之稱的加維拉（Pablo Paez Gavira），左腳拉弓射破對手大門。這位穿上10號球衣的小前鋒，踢至31分鐘憑個人技術，用他不擅長的右腳再建一功，最終以2:0勝出，闖入決賽。<br />\n<br />\n巴塞這班小將，最後有多少個日後能成材，大家請拭目以待。<br />\n<br />\n相關片段：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CvbIAaEgKjc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCvbIAaEgKjc&d=jYQxgPNCiBBMWRoR2vEy0AT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=aff9ffe5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CvbIAaEgKjc</a><br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : YouTube截圖"},{"pid":"d30023d573c6de77872bcaec97bcf69bf79da108","tid":60144,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:17:08.000Z","msg":"巴d青訓真係好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0ad5f7521b2f63564a79cd1c6329fd7dcc16eb4","tid":60144,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:20:08.000Z","msg":"又有新美斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e87ee5873503cfbf2fb74df7309d9c847bbffd18","tid":60144,"uid":1991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:23:30.000Z","msg":"10號